-- S&P 500 Stocks With Biggest Gap Between Market Price, Estimate
-- B y   W e n d y   S o o n g
-- 2012-07-06T14:48:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-06/s-p-500-stocks-with-biggest-gap-between-market-price-estimate.html
The following table shows the companies in
the  Standard & Poor’s 500 Index (SPX)  with the biggest gaps between their stock
price and analysts’ average price estimates as of July 6.  The  average estimate  is based on data compiled by Bloomberg and
reflects forecasts for the next 12 months, a period that varies
among brokerage firms. Only companies that have at least four analyst
target prices are included.  
